Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.70,0:00:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a real mess, just like the rumors said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.00,0:00:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A graveyard of ships.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.82,0:00:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a battle here \Nduring ancient times.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.75,0:00:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Our dear ancestors sure blew each other to hell and back.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.92,0:00:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,These things barely resemble ships anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone knows the story.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.58,0:00:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Our job is to search every ship we find that looks remotely salvageable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.42,0:00:57.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ridget's orders, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,This is still a bust, however you look at it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.34,0:01:02.54,Default,,0,0,0,,The few ships that survived intact have already rusted away.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.89,0:01:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.50,0:01:06.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing really looks worth searching.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.41,0:01:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's withdraw in a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.76,0:01:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.88,0:01:11.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.06,0:01:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm below you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,How about this ship?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.25,0:01:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't look too heavily damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.74,0:01:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.52,0:01:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Good catch, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.48,0:01:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to take a closer look.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.05,0:01:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,May I go inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.75,0:01:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.80,0:02:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like a cargo vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.63,0:02:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been down here for some time,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's surprisingly well-preserved.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.16,0:02:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,A core unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.68,0:02:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We can make a new Yunboro with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.99,0:02:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Great job, Ledo!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:20.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! How's the outside?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.05,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm at the stern. No apparent damage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.53,0:02:27.70,Default,,0,0,0,,She might've been scuttled.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.70,0:02:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with the bow. It's a joy to look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.67,0:02:32.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Great! Hey, Ledo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.87,0:02:33.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.70,0:02:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course it doesn't work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you really care about, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.63,0:02:49.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Researching the ancient civilization.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.95,0:02:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"Archeology," was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.59,0:02:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.60,0:02:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If I can restore some of the data, \NI might find out more
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.25,0:03:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,about the world people lived in \Nwhen this ship was built.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.97,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be sure to bring all that stuff \Nto the surface too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.29,0:03:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.33,0:03:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Bellows!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.27,0:03:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.17,0:03:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at this! Over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.24,0:03:17.10,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a huge trench!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.94,0:03:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,We can pass under the bilge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.12,0:03:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we can pull cables \Nunder it with the Yunboros.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.85,0:03:32.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we found one heck of a haul!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.65,0:03:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP}
