Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.45,0:51:21.10,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}The truly important things are invisible to the eye
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.10,0:51:27.46,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}tsunaida sono te tsuyoku nigitta
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.10,0:51:27.46,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}That's why I held your hand
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.46,0:51:33.61,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}hon no sukoshi mae made shiranakatta kimi ga
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.46,0:51:33.61,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}I only came to know you recently,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.61,0:51:42.12,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}ima konna ni mo kakegae nai hitori natteku
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.61,0:51:42.12,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}and you're already irreplaceable to me
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.12,0:51:48.41,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}wasurenaide ne itsumo soba ni iru yo
Dialogue: 0,0:51:42.12,0:51:48.41,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}Don't forget, I'm right here
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.41,0:51:54.73,ED+,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}yorokobi mo kanashimi mo wakeaitai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.41,0:51:54.73,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(150,150)\blur0.5}I want to share everything with you
